<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l21">Aufſeſʒ <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vvıe Jn etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für den <expan>lantfr<ex>id</ex></expan> geladen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l22">etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr gnade <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l23"><expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> der merteıl ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht anheim ſeın . vvıe dar = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l24">umb ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır des C . <expan>lawgıng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> freẅnd . vnd den Ott <expan>grefemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l25">der ſıch Seıcʒen Slehen darinn gemechtıgt hat für vns beſant vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l26">durch <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jn gerett / daʒ ſıe <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> klag gen dem </ab>
