<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsesz <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        wie in etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für den <expan>lantfr<ex>id</ex></expan>
                        geladen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr gnade <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        daz <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> der merteil zu <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim sein. Wie darumb so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir des <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Lawging<ex>er</ex>s</expan> frewnd und den Ott
                                <expan>Grefemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, der sich Seiczen Slehen darinn
                        gemechtigt hat, für uns besant und durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in gerett, daz sie
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> klag gen dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Aufsess zu disem mal abgetan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fallen lassen. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Nicolai. </ab>
</div>
